PostgreSQL AGE Operator
This product includes software originally developed by Crunchy Data Solutions, Inc.
and contributors as part of the Postgres Operator (PGO) project.

Original project: https://github.com/CrunchyData/postgres-operator
Copyright: 2017-2025 Crunchy Data Solutions, Inc.
License: Apache License 2.0

The PostgreSQL AGE Operator is a derivative work that extends the original
Postgres Operator with Apache AGE graph database functionality. The original
Postgres Operator source code is available under the Apache License 2.0.

This derivative work maintains compatibility with the Apache License 2.0
and includes attribution to the original creators as required by the license.

Apache AGE integration and modifications are additions to the original work
and are distributed under the same Apache License 2.0 terms.

The original Postgres Operator provided the foundation for:
- Kubernetes operator architecture
- PostgreSQL cluster management
- High availability features
- Backup and recovery functionality
- Security and TLS implementation
- Monitoring integration
- Container orchestration patterns

